The paper discusses the implementation of a recommender system for online dating, which involves information retrieval (IR) and user interaction (HC) with multimedia profiles (MM). The paper also mentions the lack of work in this area, indicating a need for research in social computing (SI) and natural language processing (CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IR, followed by cs.SI, cs.HC, cs.CL, and cs.MM.
